&lt;h2 id="jubilee-stone-inscription">Jubilee Stone inscription
&lt;/h2>&lt;div style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 10px;">
1282 FT&lt;br>
BUCKLAND BEACON&lt;br>
A BEACON FIRE ONE OF A CHAIN&lt;br>
WAS LIT HERE BY THE PARISHIONERS&lt;br>
OF BUCKLAND-IN-THE-MOOR&lt;br>
